  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\nHi I'd love to propose the OZ contract to standardize the Minting and Burning as per [EIP-5679](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-5679). The EIP has been drafted with OZ's ERC-20, ERC-721 and ERC-1155 in mind.\r\nThe major change that is needed for current OZ contract to comply with the draft of EIP-5679 are\r\n\r\n- EIP-20 Mintable and Burnable to also respond to EIP-165 identifiers\r\n- EIP-721 Mintable and Burnable to also respond to EIP-165 identifiers\r\n- EIP-1155 Mintable and Burnbale to respond to EIP-165 identifiers plus change `mint` to `safeMint`, change `mintBatch` to `safeMintBatch`.\r\n\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\nSee https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-5679\r\n",
